wikipedia_page.main: Anthony Eustrel (12 October 1902 – 2 July 1979) was an English actor.Eustrel made guest appearances on television programs such as Perry Mason, Maverick, Peter Gunn, 77 Sunset Strip, My Favorite Martian, Hogan's Heroes and Get Smart.Eustrel died in Woodland Hills, California. His ashes are inurned at Chapel of the Pines Crematory.
